title: Millie's Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A breakfast, lunch, coffeehouse, and diner kind of place. While the menu features many American style dishes with meat, there are vegan and vegetarian choices (but not labeled well): black bean burger, garden patty burger, tofu scramble, soy chorizo in burrito. Has soymilk for coffee drinks. Same owners as Naturewell juice bar/shop in Silverlake.
